div.withSidebar
    #[frag sidebar]

    div#main.content
        p
            "kftc is a complete revamp of the [standard FTC library](https://github.com/ftctechnh/ftc_app) in a way that makes it much more kotlin friendly, while also adding many useful utilities and fixing many annoyances and issues with the standard library."

        h2 < "Features"
        a(name: "features")
        p
            "Kotlin features many useful libraries and utilities, such as:"
            ul.nostyle
                li < "A revamped OpMode lifecycle"
                li < "A build-in configuration framework"
                li < "An asynchronous task management system"
                li < "Better hardware access and extension systems"